query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 100 AND q.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('.net-core',
'compression',
'encoding',
'hex',
'html-parsing',
'hyperledger-fabric',
'junit4',
'kendo-grid',
'logstash',
'margin',
'mocking',
'react-redux',
'tags');
